{"tid":1801403,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"德福單細胞便衣搞事製暴製亂","createTime":"2019-12-28T15:10:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T16:50:59.000Z","uid":329239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"089fc6ad0a3ad5f2e4c92d3dff403e8af2cfe697","tid":1801403,"uid":329239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:10:40.000Z","msg":"1955-1956 <br />\n本來呢個時間仲係撚緊便衣單細胞生物,之後佢地準備喺背囊攞胡椒出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5tFpvCu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5tFpvCu.jpg&h=d9029d19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n---<br />\ne個時間1957左右,起最前排嘅兩個手足畀人stop and search, 本來呢段時間仲未畀佢哋製暴製亂. 就算stop and search之後佢哋都未必直接出嚟製亂.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ge5T8qt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGe5T8qt.gif&h=fbcf646e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n---<br />\n 但係突然右邊一堆單細胞便衣喺度搞白色衫手足<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UB3baEA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUB3baEA.gif&h=660d94f8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n再之後到呢兩個gif,時間差唔多同一刻發生, 灰色便衣單細胞想推開個阿伯;大聲呼喝行開.<br />\n手足上前推開灰色便衣單細胞,避免嗰隻單細胞生物毆打伯伯.<br />\n再過幾秒後有兩個手足沖咗出嚟救援,不過唔cut啦,就係呢度開始畀咗機會佢製暴製亂,亂咁咬人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLaQrej.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLaQrej.gif&h=8ca77ba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w7DFOsx.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw7DFOsx.gif&h=1d76b159&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n單細胞便衣細制停咗某啲手足,20幾秒內防暴已經沖曬入嚟.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vzVpvJR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvzVpvJR.gif&h=24e6f223&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反思</span></strong></span></span><br />\n兩個手足比人stop and search嘅時候表現十分冷靜, 之前只係轉身慢慢行完全表現到佢心態極度平衡,去商場shopping嘅應有態度,臨危不亂. 同志們好好學習呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地畀便衣stop and search之後我哋可以忍下手先,一個手足畀佢捉去玩弄48都嫌多.有記者睇住search完咩都冇佢哋係吹唔撚脹,可以繼續shopping同撚便衣單細胞.<br />\n<br />\n就算手足唔出手佢哋都會''有理由''叫埋防暴入商場,咁都幾乎任務完成. (兩個救援出手嗰度冇cut到,不過灰色單細胞嗰度可以唔使出手, 後續兩個救援都被咬, <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以</span>班便衣出手stop and search先都唔好跟佢嘅節奏畀佢製暴製亂,順手咬幾個手足)<br />\n<br />\n 其實最希望和你shop複製到26號moko,班單細胞生物最後淨係咬到個冇帶身份證嘅,出去嗰陣時肯定嬲到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67fe943723dbd736cdb20e72c3f0e84dd91a9d6b","tid":1801403,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T15:11:54.000Z","msg":"投票： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhDfcr3wCsprrvnC37&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=775919fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37</a><br />\n<br />\n【最後4日】全民票選十八區區議會主席與發言人－民主統戰部<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800922</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phk5doO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fphk5doO.jpg&h=40b71bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n投票： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhDfcr3wCsprrvnC37&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=775919fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37</a><br />\n快啲入黎投票呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea4289d7df6227cf0